  - ai-tools
  - observability
  - python
abstract: >
  rewind is a time-travel debugger and shareable replay for Claude Code
  sessions. It captures every prompt, tool call, file edit, and cost into
  a per-session SQLite store with content-addressed file snapshots,
  presents the session as a scrubbable timeline, restores the file system
  to any prior point with `rewind goto`, and exports a privacy-masked
  Markdown transcript suitable for sharing.
